<reference id="hwcontrol" xml:lang="en-us">
    <title><xmlelement>hwcontrol</xmlelement></title>
  <shortdesc>A hardware control is a key, button, switch, <ph
      rev="review-d">indicator,</ph> or other <ph rev="review-d"
      >physical</ph> device that controls a piece of hardware.</shortdesc>
